replies.body:
Hi,

I had the same issue, with the "Trying to reconnect" after logging in. I found out that the tool "Leatrix Latency Fix" was the problem. It usualy tweak your Registry for a slighly better and stable Ping, while it changes the way Packets were send from your Network. Anyway, after I removed the tool, League is running normal again.

Hopefully this can help some more of you guys.{{sticker:sg-ahri-2}}
